  "comment": {
    "text": "This is a toast message confirming that an AI provider's settings have been successfully updated. It appears after a user saves changes to an AI provider. The `{{aiProvider}}` variable will be replaced with the localized name of the AI provider (e.g., \"AI Provider\").",
